cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech synthesis using Deep Learning-based algorithms.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper specifically focuses on speech synthesis and the variability in speech of different speakers, styles, and emotions.
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing speech signals to synthesize speech with a small dataset.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses Deep Learning-based algorithms for speech synthesis and fine-tuning.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the application of AI techniques for speech synthesis.
